{"tid":1501630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(玩命）澳門出現連儂牆","createTime":"2019-08-24T12:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T06:45:06.000Z","uid":43650,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1aff80259a16b5996be2762229bceed6f5922eaa","tid":1501630,"uid":43650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCMJZAQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCMJZAQ.jpg&h=f7e44365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門南環湖旁牆上出現「連儂牆」<br />\n目前司警及政府人員已到現場調查<br />\n<br />\n澳門巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw小心行事 香港加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f41d972315f95a324b22bf87cf6a2522395c5f","tid":1501630,"uid":43650,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"南灣湖廣場今日出現一幅「連儂牆」，連儂牆上寫有「五大訴求缺一不可」、「澳門人加油，香港人加油」、「不要小圈子選舉」等字句，而牆的下方亦擺放了便條紙及筆供人填寫。期間有軍裝及便衣警員到場截查兩男兩女中學生，在調查逾1小時後，4人獲准離開，沒有任何人被捕，而連儂牆最終亦被清走。另外，有記者到場採訪時，被司警要求出示身份證，並收走其身份證約20分鐘後才獲發還。<br />\n四名學生均表示，自己並不是「連儂牆」的製作者，其中一名被警方截查的女學生表示，自己只是路經該處見到有「連儂牆」，就在連儂牆上寫上加油打氣的字句，並在附近坐下，之後就被警方截查。對於被警方截查超過一小時，她表示感到無奈及奇怪，而警方亦一直未有解釋截查她們的原因。她又指，牆上原本有侮辱他人的字句，但她們看到之後就將之撕下，「其實已經丟咗好多張。」<br />\n而另一名被截查的男學生則指，是從網上看到澳門有「連儂牆」，認為本澳很難得有機會藉「連儂牆」去發聲，想過來看看，然後就被警察截查。他表示，自己從近期香港所發生的事件中，看到港澳兩個特別行政區之間的對比，「澳門呢個地方太過唔聽人講，好多事都唔貼地，離民意好遠。我哋就想借呢啲嘅渠道，將我哋嘅意見話畀政府聽，同埋畀多啲人見到。」他亦強調，自己只是一位想澳門好的青年人，不希望澳門亂，期望以和平的方式聲援其他地方。<br />\n4名中學生最終在下午3點半後獲准離開，而記者在大約下午4點返回現場時，發現連儂牆已被人清走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DzkyCvQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDzkyCvQ.jpg&h=3e178744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://aamacau.com/2019/08/24/%E5%8D%97%E7%81%A3%E6%B9%96%E7%8F%BE%E3%80%8C%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86%E3%80%8D-%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E8%AD%A6%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5%E5%9B%9B%E5%AD%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamacau.com%2F2019%2F08%2F24%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B9%2596%25E7%258F%25BE%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586%25E3%2580%258D-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2588%25AA%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25AD%25B8%2F&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=5ce79712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://aamacau.com/2019/08/24/%E5%8D%97%E7%81%A3%E6%B9%96%E7%8F%BE%E3%80%8C%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86%E3%80%8D-%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E8%AD%A6%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5%E5%9B%9B%E5%AD%B8/</a>"},{"pid":"92ab2ea14628f6693837d372ebc4e7958c98f9a9","tid":1501630,"uid":43650,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:24:38.000Z","msg":"唔講以為兇殺案 幾張memo嚇到澳共瀨晒屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cd1e0b95b9a6901738948ca32f5ad1573f680c","tid":1501630,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1aff80259a16b5996be2762229bceed6f5922eaa","tid":1501630,"uid":43650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCMJZAQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCMJZAQ.jpg&h=f7e44365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門南環湖旁牆上出現「連儂牆」<br />\n目前司警及政府人員已到現場調查<br />\n<br />\n澳門巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw小心行事 香港加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 